      <h3>Community Glossary</h3>
      <dl>
        <dt>PP</dt><dd>Pedalpalooza — the flagship event within Bike Summer</dd>
        <dt>MMR</dt><dd>Midnight Mystery Ride</dd>
        <dt>BonB</dt><dd>Breakfast on the Bridges</dd>
        <dt>WNBR</dt><dd>World Naked Bike Ride</dd>
        <dt>No-drop</dt><dd>Ride waits for all participants; no one gets left behind</dd>
        <dt>Corking</dt><dd>Riders blocking traffic at intersections so the group flows through</dd>
        <dt>R2R</dt><dd>Ride to the ride — biking to the starting point</dd>
        <dt>VKS</dt><dd>Vera Katz Statue, Eastbank Esplanade — common meeting point</dd>
      </dl>
